  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency autoprefixer to v7.1.6",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer\">autoprefixer</a> from <code>v7.1.5</code> to <code>v7.1.6</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>postcss/autoprefixer</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"716\">7.1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/f3a633e0ba8ea984eea7666bce255f8f3f84ad7e\"><code>f3a633e</code></a> Release 7.1.6 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/c754a9cbbf396a8793777b9d0151d670c8a35f8a\"><code>c754a9c</code></a> Add warning for multiple control comments</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/001995840d7f60fcb5dbf68033d991d9930b4220\"><code>0019958</code></a> Add warning for having browserslist option</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/8d457bd81f92516de7a368b70da7dc33767ff96c\"><code>8d457bd</code></a> Fix rare case in indent changes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/0a5d38d4025677f60939dfb274419a95011cc5e6\"><code>0a5d38d</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
